      <title>日本前领导人批评岸田，称该党需要改变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/former-japan-leader-criticizes-kishida-says-party-needs-change</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本前任首相岸田文雄在周日接受采访时表示，他对执政党秘密资金丑闻的糟糕处理引发了选民的不信任，并表示即将举行的党魁选举需要改变现状。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/former-japan-leader-criticizes-kishida-says-party-needs-change</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 03:17:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
